# âŸ Null Lens

**The missing protocol between user requests and AI actions.**  
Standardized intent parsing for every AI system.  
Converts any input into a deterministic schema â€” **[Motive] [Scope] [Priority]**.

---

## ğŸ§© What it does

Null Lens turns unstructured natural-language input into a fixed three-line intent block:

```
[Motive] â€” what the user wants to achieve
[Scope] â€” where the request applies (context or domain)
[Priority] â€” what must be done first or resolved
````

One ambiguous paragraph in â†’ three structured fields out.

