## ğŸ§  Best Practices

* **One call per semantic input** â€” send full text in `messages[0].content`.
* **Persist outputs** â€” store Motive / Scope / Priority as fields in your DB.
* **Cache identical inputs** â€” identical input â†’ identical output.
* **Use Lens before RAG / agents** â€” treat its output as your canonical intent layer.
* **Test with messy inputs** â€” long emails, transcripts, logs; the schema holds.

