## â“ FAQ

**Q:** Is Lens stateful?
**A:** No â€” each call is independent. Inputs are transient and not stored.

**Q:** Is the output deterministic?
**A:** Yes. Same input â†’ same 3-line output. Determinism by design.

**Q:** Will the format ever change?
**A:** Never. The `[Motive] / [Scope] / [Priority]` schema is permanent.

**Q:** Average latency?
**A:** ~1â€“5 s per call, depending on region and load.

